144static loaded_module *loaded_modules = NULL;
145static size_t num_loaded_modules = 0;

147void *
148yasm_load_module(yasm_module_type type, const char *keyword)
149{
150 size_t i;
151 module *modules;
152 size_t n;
153
154 /* Look for the module/symbol, first in loaded modules */
155 if (loaded_modules) {
156 for (i=0; i<num_loaded_modules; i++) {
157 if (loaded_modules[i].type == type &&
158 yasm__strcasecmp(loaded_modules[i].keyword, keyword) == 0)
159 return loaded_modules[i].data;
160 }
161 }
162
163 modules = module_types[type].m;
164 n = module_types[type].n;
165 for (i=0; i<n; i++) {
166 if (yasm__strcasecmp(modules[i].keyword, keyword) == 0)
167 return modules[i].data;
168 }
169
170 return NULL;
171}

173void
174yasm_register_module(yasm_module_type type, const char *keyword, void *data)
175{
176 loaded_modules =
177 yasm_xrealloc(loaded_modules,
178 (num_loaded_modules+1)*sizeof(loaded_module));
179 loaded_modules[num_loaded_modules].type = type;
180 loaded_modules[num_loaded_modules].keyword = keyword;
181 loaded_modules[num_loaded_modules].data = data;
182 num_loaded_modules++;
183}

185static void
186yasm_list_one_module(yasm_module_type type, void *data,
187 void (*printfunc) (const char *name, const char *keyword))
188{
189 yasm_arch_module *arch;
190 yasm_dbgfmt_module *dbgfmt;
191 yasm_objfmt_module *objfmt;
192 yasm_listfmt_module *listfmt;
193 yasm_parser_module *parser;
194 yasm_preproc_module *preproc;
195
196 switch (type) {
197 case YASM_MODULE_ARCH:
198 arch = data;
199 printfunc(arch->name, arch->keyword);
200 break;
201 case YASM_MODULE_DBGFMT:
202 dbgfmt = data;
203 printfunc(dbgfmt->name, dbgfmt->keyword);
204 break;
205 case YASM_MODULE_OBJFMT:
206 objfmt = data;
207 printfunc(objfmt->name, objfmt->keyword);
208 break;
209 case YASM_MODULE_LISTFMT:
210 listfmt = data;
211 printfunc(listfmt->name, listfmt->keyword);
212 break;
213 case YASM_MODULE_PARSER:
214 parser = data;
215 printfunc(parser->name, parser->keyword);
216 break;
217 case YASM_MODULE_PREPROC:
218 preproc = data;
219 printfunc(preproc->name, preproc->keyword);
220 break;
221 }
222}

224void
225yasm_list_modules(yasm_module_type type,
226 void (*printfunc) (const char *name, const char *keyword))
227{
228 size_t i;
229 module *modules;
230 size_t n;;
231
232 /* Go through available list, and try to load each one */
233 if (loaded_modules) {
234 for (i=0; i<num_loaded_modules; i++)
235 yasm_list_one_module(type, loaded_modules[i].data, printfunc);
236 }
237
238 modules = module_types[type].m;
239 n = module_types[type].n;
240 for (i=0; i<n; i++)
241 yasm_list_one_module(type, modules[i].data, printfunc);
242}
